OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAn overcast start with periods
OL,6,Fof rain, heavy at times and combining
OL,7,Fwith gales to bring decidedly un-
OL,8,FSpring like weather. Clearing to
OL,9,Fblustery showers in western districts
OL,10,Flate morning, elsewhere for the
OL,11,Fafternoon, as showers turn wintry
OL,12,Facross higher ground.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FBlustery showers pushing
OL,15,Facross the area on strong to gale west
OL,16,Fto southwest winds. Outbreaks will be
OL,17,Ffrequent, occasionally heavy and
OL,18,Fturning wintry to quite low levels.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
