OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FShowers continuing, frequent
OL,6,Fin the west, occasional in east, but
OL,7,Foutbreaks lighter than Thursday night.
OL,8,FBest of the brighter spells expected
OL,9,Faround the eastern coastal fringes.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,12,Ffor Saturday focused in west. Rain
OL,13,Fearly Sunday, clearing to blustery
OL,14,Fshowers by afternoon, these wintry
OL,15,Facross hills. Scattered showers then
OL,16,Fperiods of rain for Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
